&lt;p&gt;however, as i have come to find out (not before a whole hour of debugging): it ... depends?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://rodigu.github.io/posts/data-eng/tsql-between/"&gt;Read more…&lt;/a&gt; (2 min remaining to read)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>databases</category><category>sql</category><guid>https://rodigu.github.io/posts/data-eng/tsql-between/</guid><pubDate>Tue, 16 Dec 2025 20:10:00 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>